name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.namenode.max-num-blocks-to-log
description:
Puts a limit on the number of blocks printed to the log by the Namenode
    after a block report.

name: mapreduce.job.end-notification.retry.attempts
description:
The number of times the submitter of the job wants to retry job
    end notification if it fails. This is capped by
    mapreduce.job.end-notification.max.attempts

name: dfs.storage.policy.satisfier.queue.limit
description:
Storage policy satisfier queue size. This queue contains the currently
    scheduled file's inode ID for statisfy the policy.
    Default value is 1000.

name: dfs.client.deadnode.detection.idle.sleep.ms
description: The sleep time of DeadNodeDetector per iteration.

name: dfs.datanode.handler.count
description: The number of server threads for the datanode.
